,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T13:56:48.000Z","msg":"宜家講到明係唱pop為主,試下新野新風格,不時有d古怪歌,好似standard,本を読む,ヘブンな気分<br />\n2016隻大碟好多歌都參考歐美歌,我自己都一般<br />\n反而幾鐘意2015大碟<br />\n<br />\n我唔係好識分pop同rock,不過我諗不時都會出番d較rock,或者叫較貼近以前既風格既歌,好似Freedom Fighters,お願いナビゲーション<br />\n<br />\n至於haru把聲傷過,已經冇可能好似以前咁唱,雖然宜家把聲冇咁硬朗冇咁raw,但係好聽左既.唱瞬間果d歌能冇咁有feel,不過岩唱慢歌pop歌. btw,黎緊3-7月50幾場live,唔知頂唔頂得住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n至於樣,排牙就大執過,箍左牙都4-5年,有排仲戴鋼牙live.眼皮就唔知,可能有割掛"},{"pid":"88dcafdebc849c083ad20fda4a0f3391f754e58a","tid":135474,"uid":34105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T14:11:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中意departure 同rainy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nkoe<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c91337c9fe7fe922254dd56cac8a84ef3c6ddaf","tid":135474,"uid":37125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T15:00:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f67cdbffbca0e4e68b2cee3bdeee02931ef540c","tid":135474,"uid":37125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T16:57:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c37a06e8bdfe9c95e65f1a2d66b38544d4032c16","tid":135474,"uid":37125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T18:52:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d96680583c241ae0d5656c9d814a337506caa846","tid":135474,"uid":37125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T04:21:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"216df8385f56693944fef73bae2a7ef57253552e","tid":135474,"uid":1343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T04:34:44.000Z","msg":"鼓手最索<br />\n都係唔係fans 唔知咩名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"